cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.IT 

The paper discusses the implementation of Active Queue Management Technique for providing Quality of Service (QoS) using Network Processor(NP) based router to enhance multimedia applications. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also focuses on multimedia applications, which makes cs.MM (Multimedia) a likely category. The paper also discusses congestion control, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses load distribution schemes and prioritized flows, which are related to cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper discusses the performance evaluation of the proposed system, which falls under cs.IT (Information Theory).
